p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Seriously though, I used to solo Seafury Cyclops when they were still dark blue...just made an animation pet, buff it up, pull with tash, let it hit me to engage pet, back up, slow, DoT, med then nuke.  Med up while pet heals, rinse and repeat.  Not saying its the fastest exp in the world, but little chance of adds and the gems were great for an aspiring jeweler.<br>
<br>
Naturally Dire Charm is the best way to go..just get yourself regen 3 along the way!<br>
<br>
