Head to sg. get up a 55pet, buff em up. I start with mez mob, tash, slow, cripple, have runes up, have root up, break mez with dot, root, run. sit med, keep casting bedlam or other such spells on pet. Is really slow but can be done. also after first mob is dead, you can head to the next island. I start off with mez again, then i swim over, if you do it right none of the sea horses will agro. Then i just continue like the last, tash slow ect. Also get some good drops here, ToV quest stones and netted kelp gear. There I said it, you can use that technique of fighting with a summoned pet on lots of mobs, just be sure you have a safety net. Also be aware of the mobs that cast, they don't mez easy, but if you mana tap em first they can be dealt with. Also each mob I had to slow twice, can time it to about two bubs into mobs health cast slow again and you should do ok. <br>
lol didn't start charming with confidence till i was 62, even with maxed charisma. Charm breaks and it's usualy chanter buffee.<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :eek --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/eek.gif ALT=":eek"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->     <br>
